{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"eabd7f0bae","title":"转发湖南省委扩大会议情况汇报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a61067e59b","index":1,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":3,"articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"e9aa33d64c","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":2,"articleId":"eabd7f0bae"}],"tags":[{"id":"5fd56865b0","name":"彭真","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"60c4fb018d","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一写在中共湖南省委办公厅1959年8月30日关于省委扩大会议情况给中央的电话汇报上；本篇二、三写在湖南省委9月1日关于省委扩大会议情况给毛泽东并中央的书面报告上。"},{"id":"030c4014c2","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记。"},{"id":"43593749de","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共湖南省委办公厅1959年8月30日的电话汇报。汇报说，省委扩大会议第一阶段的主要内容是：一、确定了今年主要产品的跃进指标。二、突出地抓了当前的生产。三、对于生活安排问题，强调当前主要是加强对农民的思想教育。口号是：鼓足干劲搞生产，精打细算过日子。四、放手发动群众，大搞群众运动，把轰轰烈烈的群众运动与扎扎实实的具体措施结合起来。"},{"id":"92ccfe6ec9","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共湖南省委1959年9月1日关于省委扩大会议第一阶段情况给毛泽东并中央的书面报告。报告补充说，这次会议提出了抓好当前工作的几个关键：第一，迅速将党的八届八中全会精神贯彻到一切工作中去。第二加强领导，把轰轰烈烈的群众运动和扎扎实实的具体措施结合起来。第三，坚持政治挂师，开展大规模的社会主义竞赛运动。第四，领导干部深入第一线，指挥生产。"},{"id":"4572b5f083","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。"},{"id":"9cdbc29737","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5f8f7ccabe","type":"title","text":"转发湖南省委扩大会议情况汇报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"60c4fb018d","type":"paragraph","text":"彭真同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"030c4014c2","type":"paragraph","text":"此件时可转各省、市、区党委参考。同时印发军委扩大会及外事会议各同志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"43593749de","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"92ccfe6ec9","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二日毛泽东全集第四十二卷","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"4572b5f083","type":"paragraph","text":"此件“发各省、市、区党委参考。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"9cdbc29737","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"be6c71c13f","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年九月三日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"33cb247162","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"},{"id":"5b7fec80a1","type":"paragraph","text":"刘问、彭真同志阅，尚昆办，另印如前示","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae"}],"page":{"id":"d303e84d20","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"eabd7f0bae","start":334,"end":335}}}},"__N_SSG":true}